      "content": "it's just hard to see how anything could \"get better\" when the thing that made me *me* is gone. people say \"it will pass\" or \"find a new path\" but they don't get it. there is no other path for me. i feel like i've already reached the end of my rope, and the thought of starting all over, or even just dragging myself through another single day of this failure... it just feels impossible. it feels like the only way to actually get some peace and silence is to just... let go of everything. i'm just so incredibly done with fighting.",
